<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Student's Report Tracker</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'pages', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
  </head>

  <body>

    <%= render "navbar" %>

    <% if notice %>
      <div class="message">
        <p class="notice"><%= notice %></p>
      </div>
    <% elsif alert %>
      <div class="message">
        <p class="alert message"><%= alert %></p>
      </div>
    <% end %>
    
    <header>
      <h1>Student's Report Tracker</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="main">
      <p>
        This application is specifically build for <b>Helena Catal√†</b> to track her students activities in English.
      </p>

      <p>
        This application will help her collect the personal data of her students as well as collect their grades. Finally she will be able to get a record of the student's activities and progress in each areas of the English Language.
      </p>

      <p>
        <em>Note: Only Helena is able to access the data in this website.</em>
      </p>
    </div>
    
  </body>
</html>
